"""Tests for module-autologin-tests360.

Asserts:
- A fresh token can be redeemed exactly once.
- Reusing a token returns the "used" outcome.
- Expired tokens return the "expired" outcome.
- Unknown tokens return the "invalid" outcome.
- Every attempt logs an AutoLoginUsage row.
- The endpoint is mounted only when the module is active.

Skipped when module-autologin-tests360 is not active.
"""

